&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Finance, Economics, or a related field strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-3 years of professional experience in financial reporting and analysis, forecasting, budgeting, and planning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a startup or high-growth environment is strongly preferred; background in DTC, retail, e-commerce, or consumer goods is a plus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in financial analysis methods and concepts to prepare forecasts, cash flows and perform analyses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to analyze and extract data from databases, build dynamic tables, and generate accurate reports to support financial analysis, forecasting, budgeting, and decision-making.&amp;nbsp;

